1 Siemens without SHS.

SIEMENS SUSTAINABILIT Y REPORT 2023 45

The Decarbonization field of action commits us to reducing upstream emissions in our supply chain. As part of this effort, Siemens has set a target to reduce CO2e emissions generated in our supply chain by 20% by 2030 compared to 2020. We also aim to achieve Net Zero emissions in our supply chain by 2050.1